#'   a list-column of 3-column matrices of persistence data
#'   to a list-column of 1-row matrices of vectorizations.
#' 

#' 
#' @template step-vpd-details
#' 
#' @section Engine:
#' 
#' The tropical coordinates vectorization deploys
